FBIS3-49043 "dreeu003aa_94006" FBIS-EEU-94-003 Document Type:Daily Report 5 January 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS UN Commander Asks To Be Relieved of Duties LD0401163394 Paris France-Inter Radio Network in French 1600 GMT 4 Jan 93 LD0401163394 Paris France-Inter Radio Network Language: French Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] General Briquemont, commander of the Blue Helmets in Bosnia, who criticized UN policy in the former Yugoslavia last week, has asked to be relieved of his duties. The Belgian defense minister has denied that pressure was put on him following his statements last week. [passage omitted]
